        [
          "Classification",
          "Higher Education",
          "Blended Learning",
          "Success in Lab Assessments",
          "Pass (1) vs Fail (0)",
          "282 students",
          "3 Programming Courses: CS2, SH1, PF2",
          "Student Characteristics, Academic History, Programming Submissions, LMS logs",
          "[Distance, CAO Points, MAth LC, Avg. Grade, Exam Course Year, Results Wx, Cumulative Wx, Lab Attendance Wx, Time Wx, Lab Access Wx, Hour Access Wx, Checking Wx, On/of Campus Wx, Week(end) Wx]",
          "Every Week (Before Assignment Submission)",
          "The different features were extracted on a course-specific perspective.\n\nContent of exercises or assignments specifically was not considererd because the specifics differ signifcantly from year to year.\n\nDuring Cross-Validation, the authors selected their top 10 features for every week.\n\n",
          "Linear SVM, Gaussian SVM, Random Forest, Decision Tree, kNN, Logistic Regression",
          "10-Fold Cross-Validation",
          "CS2-Fail\n{F1-Score: 0.7450 - kNN, Precision: 0.7141 - kNN, Recall: 0.8103 - kNN}\n\nCS2-Pass\n{F1-Score: 0.5981 - kNN, Precision: 0.6880 - kNN, Recall: 0.5874 - kNN}\n\nSH1-Fail\n{F1-Score: 0.6777 - Linear SVM, Precision: 0.7141  - Linear SVM, Recall: 06954 - Linear SVM}\n\nSH1-Pass\n{F1-Score: 0.4161 - Linear SVM, Precision: 0.4553 - Linear SVM, Recall: 0.4282 - Linear SVM}\n\nPF2-Fail\n{F1-Score: 0.6673 - Decision Tree, Precision: 0.6858 - Decision Tree, Recall: 0.6954 - Decision Tree}\n\nPF2-Pass\n{F1-Score: 0.5500 - Decision Tree, Precision: 0.5862 - Decision Tree, Recall: 0.5964 - Decision Tree}",
          "Author create a set of models that predicts succes in programming assignment for every week.\n\nThis was an opt-in system. Students who participated were not only part of the early warning system but also participated in a sub-sequent recommender prototype.\n\n",
          "Specific to programming content and submissions.\n\nRelatively small sample size."
        ]
      ],
      "index": 7
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1e24750c-f3ba-809d-ba9b-ef6b783a9707",
      "heading": "Summary Table PRED",
      "rows": [
        [
          "Context",
          "Teaching Method",
          "Recommender System Type",
